1
00:00:00,233 --> 00:00:01,233
Alright.

2
00:00:02,469 --> 00:00:04,136
Let's just give it a shot.

3
00:00:04,137 --> 00:00:05,337
The best part about acting

4
00:00:05,338 --> 00:00:06,572
is that you can pour

5
00:00:06,573 --> 00:00:07,573
your heart into it

6
00:00:07,574 --> 00:00:08,574
without any consequences.

7
00:00:10,744 --> 00:00:12,478
Remember that feeling.

8
00:00:12,479 --> 00:00:13,380
And also,

9
00:00:13,381 --> 00:00:14,947
remember how we proved

10
00:00:14,948 --> 00:00:16,516
we're lucky to still have each other.

11
00:00:19,686 --> 00:00:20,787
Let's start.

12
00:00:25,225 --> 00:00:26,459
Then why did you turn away?

13
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,595
Why didn't you try to find a way?

14
00:00:30,463 --> 00:00:32,065
Find a way to do what?

15
00:00:33,166 --> 00:00:34,166
Like...

16
00:00:35,602 --> 00:00:37,042
finding a way for us to be together.

17
00:01:00,994 --> 00:01:02,929
Just how many necklaces do you have?

18
00:01:03,530 --> 00:01:04,864
This is just to prove

19
00:01:05,765 --> 00:01:07,433
how determined I am

20
00:01:07,434 --> 00:01:08,434
to be with you.

21
00:01:09,669 --> 00:01:11,438
One becomes two,

22
00:01:12,205 --> 00:01:13,205
then four,

23
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,040
eight,

24
00:01:15,275 --> 00:01:16,275
sixteen...

25
00:01:17,410 --> 00:01:18,578
So it's infinite.

26
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,180
It's a great deal.

27
00:01:22,515 --> 00:01:24,150
Then I guess I'm the lucky one.

28
00:01:28,254 --> 00:01:29,756
I've liked you for a long time.

29
00:01:30,557 --> 00:01:32,358
Would you be willing to turn

30
00:01:33,293 --> 00:01:35,028
this crush into a real relationship?

31
00:01:39,299 --> 00:01:40,733
Not just something online,

32
00:01:42,135 --> 00:01:44,737
but something real and tangible?

33
00:02:18,138 --> 00:02:19,806
I had no idea they were such good actors.

34
00:02:23,476 --> 00:02:25,345
That was pretty good, wasn't it?

35
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,614
I wonder if anyone recorded that.

36
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:28,981
I want to see it.

37
00:02:31,451 --> 00:02:33,051
That's because I've got great technique.

38
00:02:34,888 --> 00:02:36,422
It's not about your technique.

39
00:02:36,890 --> 00:02:38,123
It's because I was really in the moment.

40
00:02:38,124 --> 00:02:40,393
My empathy is just on another level, okay?

41
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,199
Director Qiao,

42
00:02:48,201 --> 00:02:49,135
I think we should have them

43
00:02:49,136 --> 00:02:50,837
swap roles and try it that way.

44
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,873
Sure, I'm up for it.

45
00:02:54,874 --> 00:02:55,874
Maybe we shouldn't.

46
00:02:56,943 --> 00:02:57,943
After all,

47
00:02:59,279 --> 00:03:00,947
Bai Xing doesn't have much experience.
